23:22.000 --> 23:23.440
You can't be trusted.

23:23.520 --> 23:25.640
Look, I'm just a working man.

23:25.720 --> 23:27.280
JOHN: We're gonna be watching you.

23:28.560 --> 23:31.280
-Watching your fucking house.
-I've got kids.

23:34.160 --> 23:35.280
Ethan and John.

23:39.720 --> 23:41.280
