23:55.120 --> 23:56.560
-Yes.
-Thank you.

24:00.000 --> 24:02.560
-(METAL CLANKING)
-(MEN SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)

24:13.560 --> 24:14.680
Good.

24:15.480 --> 24:16.560
Good.

24:29.400 --> 24:31.680
-Do you think he'll return?
-Tommy?

24:36.440 --> 24:37.760
He'll always come back.

24:39.880 --> 24:40.880
You speak differently when you talk...

24:40.960 --> 24:42.720
