of the things I don't know.

25:02.200 --> 25:04.280
What could you possibly not know?

25:05.520 --> 25:06.880
I wasn't educated.

25:12.920 --> 25:15.240
-At all.
-What is there to learn, after all?

25:24.080 --> 25:25.080
Goodness.

25:27.320 --> 25:29.600
