25:41.960 --> 25:44.200
Do you tell your friends
you're painting a gangster?

25:47.560 --> 25:49.120
Is that the fun in all of this?

25:50.040 --> 25:51.600
In truth, I don't have any friends.

25:53.360 --> 25:55.080
I knew everyone through my wife.

25:57.640 --> 25:58.920
When she died...

26:02.760 --> 26:03.840
Well...

26:07.640 --> 26:08.880
Look, Polly,

26:10.920 --> 26:13.320
