26:14.280 --> 26:19.040
Firstly, you have a face
full of contradictions,

26:20.200 --> 26:22.800
and it's a challenge
to capture them in one expression.

26:23.120 --> 26:25.000
-(SCOFFS)
-That's the sales pitch.

26:26.960 --> 26:32.720
The second motivation is that
I am planning to seduce you eventually

26:34.240 --> 26:36.200
and, please God, sleep with you.

26:36.640 --> 26:38.240
How would that please God?

26:38.880 --> 26:40.280
Please me.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.080
And stop.

27:24.440 --> 27:25.920
And he didn't say what he wants.

27:27.000 --> 27:28.800
When he was drunk, he said absolution.

27:29.440 --> 27:30.800
Other than that, nothing.

27:51.360 --> 27:53.360
