27:55.040 --> 27:56.920
I heard someone shot your wife.

28:02.000 --> 28:04.600
If you're looking for soldiers,
our men are all up at Apple by.

28:04.800 --> 28:06.560
I have no need for soldiers.

28:07.640 --> 28:09.080
It's not why I came here.

28:21.480 --> 28:22.480
What do you think?

28:22.800 --> 28:24.040
You're selling?

28:24.120 --> 28:25.280
Giving.

28:27.000 --> 28:28.640
-Why?
-Would you take it?

28:30.560 --> 28:31.760
I'd take it.

28:32.480 --> 28:33.680
Would you wear it?

28:33.760 --> 28:35.760
-Why would I not?
-That's my question.

28:43.440 --> 28:45.800
My wife was wearing it
the night she was shot,

28:48.800 --> 28:54.320
and I lie awake at night
at 4:00 in the fucking morning,

28:54.400 --> 28:56.800
and I blame myself for her death.

28:58.640 --> 29:00.400
I pushed some people too far.

29:02.160 --> 29:04.760
You want me to tell you
this jewel is cursed,

29:07.320 --> 29:09.600
and then her death won't be
all your fault.

29:17.440 --> 29:19.520
If I believed in the priests,

29:20.280 --> 29:22.520
