29:23.840 --> 29:26.760
but all I have is you, Madame Boswell.

29:28.280 --> 29:29.760
I have a son.

29:31.920 --> 29:33.680
I have a business.

29:34.240 --> 29:35.800
I need to get some sleep.

29:39.600 --> 29:40.960
It is cursed.

29:43.160 --> 29:46.440
I feel its curse
burning through my heart.

29:53.360 --> 29:55.280
Bless you, Tommy Shelby.

29:56.280 --> 29:58.400
You'll have good fortune from now on.

29:58.480 --> 30:00.920
-The business is done?
-It's done.

30:01.960 --> 30:04.720
You're not going to give me
one fucking clue what that was about?

30:05.360 --> 30:08.840
All religion is a foolish answer
