37:51.440 --> 37:52.840
Open your eyes.

37:53.840 --> 37:58.560
Open your eyes,
or I will cut away your fucking eyelids!

38:02.360 --> 38:04.080
Now look at me.

38:05.200 --> 38:06.880
Look at me.

38:08.840 --> 38:10.320
This is the end.

38:12.360 --> 38:13.880
This is the end.

38:20.880 --> 38:23.160
It was your tongue that gave the order.

38:26.720 --> 38:29.040
I'll take your tongue first.

38:31.760 --> 38:33.520
