38:36.080 --> 38:38.280
Then I'll take your fingers.

38:39.560 --> 38:41.480
Then your fucking toes.

38:42.880 --> 38:47.280
See, I take your balls first,
you drain too fast like you fuckers do.

38:50.080 --> 38:54.280
No, I think tongue first. Tongue first.

38:54.600 --> 38:56.240
(MUFFLED GROANING)

38:57.920 --> 38:58.920
Tongue first.

39:02.600 --> 39:04.680
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

39:05.520 --> 39:09.400
If I take your tongue,
you won't be able to explain,

39:10.480 --> 39:14.960
and I want you to explain.
I want you to fucking explain.

39:28.240 --> 39:30.440
(TOMMY BREATHING HEAVILY)

39:34.920 --> 39:36.960
(CONTINUES PRAYING)

39:47.680 --> 39:48.840
Come on, Tommy.

39:51.720 --> 39:53.720
I forget who I am.

39:54.640 --> 39:56.120
I forget who I am.

39:57.240 --> 40:00.040
I'm a Blinder.
I'll take your fucking eyes first!

40:00.280 --> 40:01.280
