and I need to know why.

43:40.440 --> 43:41.920
James Monkland.

43:42.800 --> 43:46.000
He's a Lloyds underwriter.
He's got an office on Curzon Street.

43:46.120 --> 43:48.320
Tommy, for fuck's sake,
who is it that's ahead of you?

43:49.720 --> 43:50.880
I knew I could count on you, Ada.

43:51.080 --> 43:54.240
