Do the transit deals.

45:00.280 --> 45:01.880
James Monkland, right?

45:05.400 --> 45:07.360
Good night, Ada.

45:19.880 --> 45:22.440
-James Monkland?
-Yours, sir.

45:47.920 --> 45:49.160
Who the hell are you?

45:50.920 --> 45:52.000
