46:16.440 --> 46:18.200
They have many fucking names.

46:18.280 --> 46:19.520
Shit, shit, shit.

46:20.320 --> 46:22.400
Give me the name of the informant.

46:29.000 --> 46:30.560
Mr Shelby,

46:33.040 --> 46:35.200
