-(CHUCKLES)

48:51.120 --> 48:52.120
(EXHALES)

48:55.120 --> 48:56.520
Right, then.

48:57.000 --> 48:58.520
(CHUCKLES)

48:58.600 --> 49:01.800
Let's have a cup of tea. One moment.

49:09.160 --> 49:10.160
(LAUGHS)

49:10.680 --> 49:12.920
Come on. Let's have that tea.

49:19.800 --> 49:21.320
Arthur, for fuck's sake, what is it?

49:21.400 --> 49:24.600
No. We wait for Tommy.

49:26.320 --> 49:28.000
I've got a stolen statue back there

49:28.080 --> 49:30.280
with its dick hanging out
waiting to be melted down.

49:31.160 --> 49:32.720
Tell us. Tell Tommy later.

49:32.800 --> 49:35.440
Yeah, look, he's not here.
He's not here. I'm going.

49:36.200 --> 49:37.240
-Hold your horses.
-There he is.

49:37.320 --> 49:38.680
-Bye, Curly.
-There he is.

49:38.760 --> 49:40.000
All right, what is it?

49:40.080 --> 49:41.840
Arthur's fucking giving us
all this shit.

49:41.920 --> 49:42.960
Come on. Come on.

49:43.040 --> 49:44.320
Right.

49:47.160 --> 49:49.440
Arthur, you got wire
on the fucking cork. Give it here.

49:49.520 --> 49:52.440
Bastard. Right. Gentlemen!

49:59.040 --> 50:04.520
Linda is up the swanny.
I'm gonna be a fucking dad.

50:05.040 --> 50:07.320
-Fuck off. (CHUCKLES)
-(ALL LAUGHING)

50:07.920 --> 50:10.200
Yes, Curly. Yeah.

50:11.200 --> 50:14.080
Arthur, I knew you had it in you.

50:14.600 --> 50:16.120
I knew he had it in him.

50:16.200 --> 50:17.400
September she reckons.

50:18.160 --> 50:19.680
Her tits feel different already.

50:19.760 --> 50:21.960
Yeah, that's not the only thing
that's gonna be different, brother.

50:22.160 --> 50:23.920
You're fucked now, man.

50:24.200 --> 50:25.880
Fucked. Absolutely fucked.

50:26.040 --> 50:28.200
Oh, nothing's gonna change, John.

50:29.720 --> 50:30.800
Goodbye, Arthur.

50:32.880 --> 50:36.040
-I have a meeting I have to go to.
-Yeah.

50:36.760 --> 50:38.400
Yeah, of course you do.

50:42.400 --> 50:43.520
Yeah, you...

50:45.520 --> 50:46.760
You go to, mate.

50:48.000 --> 50:49.600
Congratulations.

50:50.320 --> 50:52.360
-I'm gonna be a dad.
-Proud of you.

51:29.800 --> 51:30.800
(DOOR OPENS)

51:31.240 --> 51:33.080
Your Highness, Mr Thomas Shelby.

51:37.840 --> 51:39.640
Welcome, Mr Shelby.

51:39.720 --> 51:44.040
