52:02.600 --> 52:04.120
which some of us witnessed.

52:05.480 --> 52:06.480
(TOMMY SNIFFS)

52:09.200 --> 52:11.800
-Did you drive, Mr Shelby?
-Yes.

52:17.160 --> 52:20.120
-They say you're an expert on cars.
-Yes, I am.

52:20.200 --> 52:23.480
