What was your father's profession?

52:23.600 --> 52:26.760
Well, he told fortunes,
and he stole horses.

52:26.840 --> 52:30.080
Often, he would tell a man
that his horse would be stolen,

52:30.160 --> 52:32.680
and they would marvel at his powers
when it was.

52:38.960 --> 52:41.560
Before we eat, should we say grace?

52:46.360 --> 52:51.600
