to your evening.

53:02.400 --> 53:07.880
Grand Duchess, I must apologise
for the bad manners of my compatriot.

53:08.040 --> 53:11.200
This is a report on the mission's
progress so far. (CLEARS THROAT)

53:11.440 --> 53:13.680
